FBIS4-14486 "drsov063_d_94008" FBIS-SOV-94-063 Daily Report 31 Mar 1994 Regional Affairs Kazan Hosts Conference of Regional Law Enforcement Officers Kazan Hosts Conference of Regional Law Enforcement Officers PM3103134394 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA in Russian 31 Mar 94 First Edition p 6 PM3103134394 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA Russian BFN [Unattributed report: "Consultation"] [Text] A regional conference of leaders of Volga Region organs of prosecutor's offices, internal affairs, and counterintelligence has been held in Kazan. Representatives of Bashkiria, the Mari Republic, Mordovia, Tatarstan, Udmurtia, Chuvashia, and Nizhniy Novgorod, Orenburg, Samara, and Ulyanovsk Oblasts participated in it. The topic of the conference was the struggle against organized crime, drugs trafficking, and the illegal circulation of weapons. Measures were devised which envisage cooperation between the ministries and departments in neighboring regions. An appeal has been adopted to the Federal Assembly and the Russian Federation president to immediately produce and adopt a package of legislative acts designed to combat organized crime, corruption, drugs trafficking, and the illegal circulation of weapons.
